        Parameters:
        updateName - - Name for "update" action
        statusName - - Name for "status action"
        supportsDeletion - - User can perform delete action for files from the group
        id - - Using in order to find the group
        canBeAbsent - - If canBeAbsent == true absent files from the group will not be marked as invalid
